{"tid":210602,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"急！！！入境處職員入！！","createTime":"2017-04-21T05:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T02:47:28.000Z","uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"bc2425442f2e8566007f7c16a99091f11a402b0c","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:27:35.000Z","msg":"前幾日book完機票酒店先發覺唔見左本passport（特區）,今日去補領，見到5月10可以拎都安心,點知個職員同我講遺失要4-6星期，5月10係拎唔到，但我5月17日出發。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以指點明燈，或者係職員有計幫幫細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屎已瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d504c66f19f54c313568292573515d9d1e73e34c","tid":210602,"uid":6752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:29:30.000Z","msg":"你仲有幾星期時間反轉間屋"},{"pid":"1231141f1426e472d863885fa6998c1970c90293","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前幾日book完機票酒店先發覺唔見左本passport（特區）,今日去補領，見到5月10可以拎都安心,點知個職員同我講遺失要4-6星期，5月10係拎唔到，但我5月17日出發。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以指點明燈，或者係職員有計幫幫細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n屎已瀨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65ca08e4a5d2b82f963d04cf7fd05cce1743af0","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:31:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你仲有幾星期時間反轉間屋</blockquote><br />\n琴晚已經反轉左都冇，應該係執屋果陣唔小心掉左，15號仲見到，17號執完屋就搵唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b55658f4b2c2d5f66591573a1e7d8d963278d7","tid":210602,"uid":74209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:32:07.000Z","msg":"［唔是入境署聯員］<br />\nChing有冇申請過BNO? 攞本過期BNO去英領事館申請臨時護照，千幾蚊，4日搞掂"},{"pid":"b727533e7aa30c23157ef778e2c008ecf92f83fd","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:36:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>［唔是入境署聯員］<br />\nChing有冇申請過BNO? 攞本過期BNO去英領事館申請臨時護照，千幾蚊，4日搞掂</blockquote><br />\n岩上網都見到，就係冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6adc7c247398711470876cd69c5d915cebc3eb8","tid":210602,"uid":93713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"你係急就自己打去入境處問"},{"pid":"a53f8ad215662f13bc889200e591f5060a1dc4eb","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:41:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係急就自己打去入境處問</blockquote><br />\n打左，放飯冇人聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d47b6652148a2912ad54a50ab7edb008739316","tid":210602,"uid":88309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:53:00.000Z","msg":"正常其實都係十日左右(唔計六日同公假)，即係如果你今日申請應該係喺9號左右就有，可能佢嗰邊多人申請啩，你都係打去問一問好啲<br />\n你大約兩點至兩點半再打去啦，依家呢個鐘數應該放緊飯<br />\nTel：2824 6111"},{"pid":"5ca12db0091760a957353dff9d5b15d607d8dec6","tid":210602,"uid":15,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常其實都係十日左右(唔計六日同公假)，即係如果你今日申請應該係喺9號左右就有，可能佢嗰邊多人申請啩，你都係打去問一問好啲<br />\n你大約兩點至兩點半再打去啦，依家呢個鐘數應該放緊飯<br />\nTel：2824 6111</blockquote><br />\n仲要未計網上預約去拎呢, 而家5月頭9成都爆晒期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32c409413e02dc7e6a8fa2975c3627009b13ff84","tid":210602,"uid":74209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:56:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>［唔是入境署聯員］<br />\nChing有冇申請過BNO? 攞本過期BNO去英領事館申請臨時護照，千幾蚊，4日搞掂</blockquote><br />\n岩上網都見到，就係冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果有辦法證明係非旅行出境（公幹etc），個入境處官員信你就可做快證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我試過申請不受理啦所以就臨時BNO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a8e80f7c082d51d0825400db9364a3d802a0177","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T05:59:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常其實都係十日左右(唔計六日同公假)，即係如果你今日申請應該係喺9號左右就有，可能佢嗰邊多人申請啩，你都係打去問一問好啲<br />\n你大約兩點至兩點半再打去啦，依家呢個鐘數應該放緊飯<br />\nTel：2824 6111</blockquote><br />\n唔該巴打，晏少少再打"},{"pid":"2b5e2da8c490a5e1b5d6c62057d01a46d18222c0","tid":210602,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:02:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你仲有幾星期時間反轉間屋</blockquote><br />\n琴晚已經反轉左都冇，應該係執屋果陣唔小心掉左，15號仲見到，17號執完屋就搵唔番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想搵就搵唔到,唔要就識彈番出黎<br />\n金句黎<br />\n冷靜下慢慢仔細搵啦你<br />\n可能你屋企人放埋唔知邊度"},{"pid":"bf1fb70bc300e15386354a827430928e3c2728b1","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T06:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>［唔是入境署聯員］<br />\nChing有冇申請過BNO? 攞本過期BNO去英領事館申請臨時護照，千幾蚊，4日搞掂</blockquote><br />\n岩上網都見到，就係冇呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果有辦法證明係非旅行出境（公幹etc），個入境處官員信你就可做快證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我試過申請不受理啦所以就臨時BNO <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n冇啦啦點會有公幹証明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做緊大公司....細公司可能有機會....."},{"pid":"28c8e7e2bccfd6f84550f51ae56bc6f8aba6ff56","tid":210602,"uid":8122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T07:57:39.000Z","msg":"你可以死左條心<br />\n遺失係要耐d先拎到"},{"pid":"882d89619b2a4fdc6f54b609cd5efda70218a664","tid":210602,"uid":65917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:07:18.000Z","msg":"我之前都係唔見左護照，3月11號遞表，3月24號寄信黎叫我3月28號拎"},{"pid":"eb4cc8d50b63520c67fb40ba97de7a244a7e88ac","tid":210602,"uid":65917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:10:00.000Z","msg":"不過我係沙田到拎"},{"pid":"06d82b19449683a69d0f67b90b751484e7d7e0a2","tid":210602,"uid":62192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"留港消費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c583d7fabd9387d739f9bcf265bc55bdf11b39","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過我係沙田到拎</blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇話咩公幹係快証果d<br />\n<br />\n邊到拎都有分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ab9ff18ff1558411b59e16ad68feedefeffdfb","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T10:29:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你可以死左條心<br />\n遺失係要耐d先拎到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉，岩岩去西九入境處求個主任都係話4-6星期，話應該去唔到"},{"pid":"d4c6bd2c087e28f381301fdd9ec46539efe180be","tid":210602,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T11:23:02.000Z","msg":"夾幾百蚊比職員<br />\n佢地自然識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bd577fef7f12a63be707591b0b833609c3bd0e","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:02:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>夾幾百蚊比職員<br />\n佢地自然識做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得既話我夾左好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45609590930c9d58b69eb57361a35cc5dd251873","tid":210602,"uid":84055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:05:48.000Z","msg":"其實有冇得話係換領，唔當遺失"},{"pid":"9a1a962b4650f3b6479aeccebffb3dc7d6a66a58","tid":210602,"uid":8435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:12:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有冇得話係換領，唔當遺失</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你拎新嗰本要拎本舊嘅去換<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27dcf7a4168884387a9eb06105d548ddb1cdf4d","tid":210602,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-21T12:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有冇得話係換領，唔當遺失</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}